snippet.title: Sly Panda - Gameplay
snippet.description:
Slow down time, fire off tons of bullets and defeat dopey ghosts. 
That is what Sly Panda is all about!

- That is what you get for destroying their precious urn ... 

It's now out on itch.io!
https://elastiskalinjen.itch.io/sly-panda 

Music used:
"Rising Tide (faster)" Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
